"btn vip-btn-gold rounded-pill px-4 py-2 w-100 w-xl-auto\"\n                               >\n                                Obtener cotizaci\u00f3n\n                            <\/a>\n                        <\/li>\n\n                    \n                    \n                \n            <\/ul>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/nav>\n\n    \n    \n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-white\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0\">\n                <h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-4\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">\u00bfQu\u00e9 es el seguro comercial?<\/h2>\n                <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 3px; background: var(--secondary-color); margin-bottom: 20px;\"><\/div>\n                <div class=\"text-dark text-justify mb-4\" style=\"line-height: 1.8;\">\n                    <p>El Seguro Comercial juega un papel crucial en la protecci\u00f3n de su empresa. Act\u00faa como un escudo financiero, ofreci\u00e9ndole tranquilidad en caso de eventos imprevistos como da\u00f1os materiales, robos, incendios o responsabilidades civiles.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"d-flex gap-3 flex-wrap\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/rendez-vous\" class=\"btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-4 shadow-sm text-white fw-bold\">Hacer una cotizaci\u00f3n<\/a>\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/contact\" class=\"btn btn-outline-dark rounded-pill px-4 shadow-sm\">Cont\u00e1ctenos<\/a>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceCommerciale\/AdobeStock_663298839.jpg\" alt=\"Assurance commerciale\" class=\"section-img rounded shadow hover-lift w-100 object-fit-cover\">\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-light\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row g-4 justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3 text-warning\"><i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt fa-3x\"><\/i><\/div>\n                    <h6 class=\"fw-bold text-dark\">Futuro asegurado<\/h6>\n                    <p class=\"text-muted small mb-0\">Asegure el futuro de su empresa con un seguro comercial confiable y flexible.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3 text-warning\"><i class=\"fas fa-handshake fa-3x\"><\/i><\/div>\n                    <h6 class=\"fw-bold text-dark\">Asociaci\u00f3n S\u00f3lida<\/h6>\n                    <p class=\"text-muted small mb-0\">En asociaci\u00f3n con Trushield Assurance, ofrecemos soluciones adaptadas.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3 text-warning\"><i class=\"fas fa-file-contract fa-3x\"><\/i><\/div>\n                    <h6 class=\"fw-bold text-dark\">Protecci\u00f3n Completa<\/h6>\n                    <p class=\"text-muted small mb-0\">Nuestro seguro protege contra los riesgos financieros, los siniestros materiales y la responsabilidad civil.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3 text-warning\"><i class=\"fas fa-users-cog fa-3x\"><\/i><\/div>\n                    <h6 class=\"fw-bold text-dark\">Experiencia y Serenidad<\/h6>\n                    <p class=\"text-muted small mb-0\">Un equipo de expertos lo acompa\u00f1a. Elija la tranquilidad.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"pt-5 pb-4 bg-white\">\n    <div class=\"container text-center\">\n        <h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-0\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">Los factores que influyen en el costo<\/h2>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n<section class=\"py-5 d-flex align-items-center\" style=\"background-image: url('https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceCommerciale\/assurance-commerciale-cout.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; min-height: 500px;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-end\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-5 col-md-8\">\n                <div class=\"bg-white p-4 p-md-5 rounded shadow-lg text-center\">\n                    <p class=\"text-dark mb-0\" style=\"line-height: 1.8;\">El costo promedio de un seguro comercial var\u00eda entre $1,000 y m\u00e1s de $10,000 al a\u00f1o, dependiendo del tama\u00f1o, el tipo de empresa y su ubicaci\u00f3n.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-light\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-5\">\n            <h2 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color:var(--primary-color);\">Existen dos tipos de seguros comerciales<\/h2>\n            <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 3px; background: var(--secondary-color); margin: 15px auto;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"row g-5 justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-5\">\n                <div class=\"d-flex align-items-start bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm h-100 hover-lift\">\n                    <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceCommerciale\/risk-management_7392790.png\" width=\"70\" class=\"me-4 flex-shrink-0\" alt=\"Tous risques\">\n                    <div>\n                        <h4 class=\"fw-bold text-dark mb-2\">El seguro a todo riesgo<\/h4>\n                        <p class=\"text-muted mb-0\">Es m\u00e1s completo y cubre una amplia gama de situaciones, salvo excepciones espec\u00edficas.<\/p>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-5\">\n                <div class=\"d-flex align-items-start bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm h-100 hover-lift\">\n                    <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceCommerciale\/risk-assessment_14105612.png\" width=\"70\" class=\"me-4 flex-shrink-0\" alt=\"Risques d\u00e9sign\u00e9s\">\n                    <div>\n                        <h4 class=\"fw-bold text-dark mb-2\">El seguro de riesgos designados<\/h4>\n                        <p class=\"text-muted mb-0\">M\u00e1s econ\u00f3mico, ofrece menos protecci\u00f3n y protege de p\u00e9rdidas resultantes de situaciones espec\u00edficas.<\/p>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"text-center mt-5\">\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/contact\" class=\"btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-5 shadow-sm mt-3 text-white fw-bold\">Saber m\u00e1s<\/a>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-white\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-5\">\n            <h2 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color:var(--primary-color);\">Zona de consejos<\/h2>\n            <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 3px; background: var(--secondary-color); margin: 15px auto;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"row g-4 justify-content-center\">\n                    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<style>\n    .hover-lift {\n        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n    }\n\n    .hover-lift:hover {\n        transform: translateY(-5px);\n        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) !important;\n    }\n<\/style>\n\n<footer class=\"fo